;\">\n<td style=\"padding:12px 0;\"><span style=\"background:#2d0a0a;color:#f87171;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">&#128680; ALERT</span></td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 0;color:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">ANET</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 0;\">\n<span style=\"background:#1e1e35;color:#818cf8;font-size:9px;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:3px;display:inline-block;margin-bottom:2px;\">AI Networking</span>\n<span style=\"background:#1e1e35;color:#818cf8;font-size:9px;padding:2px 5px;border-radius:3px;display:inline-block;\">Data Center</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 0;color:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-align:right;\">$137.53</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 0;color:#ef4444;font-size:12px;text-align:right;\">&#8722;2.99%</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 0;text-align:right;\">\n<span style=\"color:#ef4444;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;display:block;\">&#8722;$24.73</span>\n<span style=\"color:#ef4444;font-size:11px;\">&#8722;12.4%</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#f8fafc;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;\">TOTAL &nbsp;<span style=\"color:#64748b;font-weight:400;\">(2 positions + $352.56 cash = $740.22)</span></td>\n<td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#f8fafc;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-align:right;\">$387.66</td>\n<td style=\"padding:10px 0;color:#ef4444;font-size:12px;text-align:right;\">&#8722;$2.44</td>\n<td style=\"padding:10px 0;text-align:right;\">\n<span style=\"color:#ef4444;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;display:block;\">&#8722;$63.73</span>\n<span style=\"color:#ef4444;font-size:11px;\">&#8722;14.1%</span>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin:4px 0 0;color:#475569;font-size:10px;\">*VERA estimated close ~$35.50. Intraday range: $34.58&#8211;$36.67, prev close $35.01, open $35.96 (web-sourced; IBKR offline). Verify exact close in broker app.</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<!-- EXIT ALERTS -->\n<tr><td style=\"background:#0f172a;padding:14px 24px 6px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#475569;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-weight:600;\">&#9656; Exit Alerts</p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"background:#1c0808;border-left:4px solid #ef4444;padding:16px 24px;border-top:1px solid #334155;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#f87171;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">&#128680; ANET &#8212; STOP $144.00 BREACHED &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Current: $137.53</p>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:12px;\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%;vertical-align:top;padding-right:8px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">Stop (BREACHED)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#ef4444;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;\">$144.00 &#10060;</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">$6.47 below stop now</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%;vertical-align:top;padding:0 8px;border-left:1px solid #3d1515;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">Real Support (live)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#fbbf24;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;\">$136.42</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">Daily horizontal &#8212; $1.11 above current</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%;vertical-align:top;padding-left:8px;border-left:1px solid #3d1515;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">TP1 &#8212; Exit All</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#10b981;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;\">$185.00</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">By Jul 25 &middot; Analyst avg $190</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;\"><strong style=\"color:#f8fafc;\">Stop re-assessment:</strong> The $144 stop was set below the 50-day MA. Price has broken through to $137.53, now sitting $1.11 above the next real structural support at $136.42 (daily horizontal). The weekly horizontal at $141.76 has been lost. <strong style=\"color:#f8fafc;\">Thesis check:</strong> ANET raised its AI fabric revenue target to $3.5B for 2026 (up from $3.25B), raised full-year guidance to $11.5B (+27.7%), and Q1 beat at $2.71B (+35.1%). Thesis is 100% intact &#8212; this is a broad tech pullback, not a company-specific break. Analyst consensus: 30 analysts, avg $190.09 (Strong Buy).</p>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#0f172a;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:14px;width:48%;vertical-align:top;border-right:1px solid #334155;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 5px;color:#ef4444;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;\">Option A &#8212; Exit now (honor stop)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Gross: 1.27 &times; $137.53 = $174.66</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Cost basis: $199.39</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Gross P&amp;L: &#8722;$24.73</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Exit commission: &#8722;$3.00</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;color:#ef4444;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;\">Net P&amp;L: &#8722;$27.73</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:11px;\">Frees $171.66 for CAPR/dry powder</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding:14px;width:48%;vertical-align:top;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 5px;color:#10b981;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;\">Option B &#8212; Hold to $185 (Jul 25)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">New stop: $135.00 (below $136.42 support)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">If reaches $185: gross +$35.56, net +$32.56</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Hard exit deadline: July 25 pre-earnings</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;color:#fbbf24;font-size:11px;\">Risk: if $136.42 breaks, losses worsen</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:11px;\">Thesis intact &middot; $190 analyst consensus</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#fbbf24;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;\">&#8594; Lean: <strong>B (hold)</strong>. Thesis intact, $136.42 support real, analyst consensus $190 is 38% above current. Stop was set below a moving average, not below real market structure. But the stop was placed for a reason. <strong>Your call.</strong></p>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr><td style=\"background:#1a1400;border-left:4px solid #f59e0b;padding:16px 24px;border-top:1px solid #334155;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#fbbf24;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;\">&#128276; VERA &#8212; PDUFA COUNTDOWN: 4 DAYS &nbsp;(July 7, 2026)</p>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:12px;\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width:25%;vertical-align:top;padding-right:6px;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">Stop (academic)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#ef4444;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">$24.50</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">Won&#8217;t catch CRL gap</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%;vertical-align:top;padding:0 6px;border-left:1px solid #3d2f00;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">TP1 (sell 50%)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#10b981;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">$55.00</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">Post-approval zone</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%;vertical-align:top;padding:0 6px;border-left:1px solid #3d2f00;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">TP2 (remaining)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#10b981;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">$78.00</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">Analyst consensus midpoint</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25%;vertical-align:top;padding-left:6px;border-left:1px solid #3d2f00;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 3px;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;text-transform:uppercase;\">Approval Prob</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#10b981;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;\">89%</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#64748b;font-size:10px;\">NEJM Phase 3 + Priority Review</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;\">Stock has slid from its pre-PDUFA run-up to ~$35.50 &#8212; classic buy-the-rumor-sell-the-news profit taking by momentum traders who rode anticipation. Insider selling by CEO Fordyce Marshall adds marginal negative sentiment but doesn&#8217;t change the FDA thesis. 14 analysts Strong Buy, avg target $78. The $24.50 stop is academic: if FDA issues a CRL, stock gaps to $10&#8211;15 on the open &#8212; no stop catches that move.</p>\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#0f172a;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n<tr>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 14px;width:32%;vertical-align:top;border-right:1px solid #334155;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 5px;color:#10b981;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;\">Hold all 6 (original plan)</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Approval (89%): 6 &times; ($55&#8211;$35.50) = +$117</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">CRL (11%): 6 &times; ($12&#8211;$35.50) = &#8722;$141</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">EV = 0.89&times;$117 &#8722; 0.11&times;$141</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0;color:#10b981;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;\">EV = +$88.62 &#10003;</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding:12px 14px;width:32%;vertical-align:top;border-right:1px solid #334155;\">\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 5px;color:#fbbf24;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;\">Trim 3 shares today</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Gross P&amp;L: 3&times;($35.50&#8722;$42) = &#8722;$19.50</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 2px;color:#94a3b8;font-size:11px;\">Commission: &#8722;$3.00</p>\n<p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;color:#ef4444;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;\">Net: &#8722;$22.50 locked in<